Well, thank you for taking the
time to attend our talk today.

00:27:14.425 --> 00:27:16.300
Hopefully, you've learned
a couple of things.

00:27:16.300 --> 00:27:19.810
And we showed you a little
bit of how to achieve success

00:27:19.810 --> 00:27:21.910
on Android TV.

00:27:21.910 --> 00:27:24.580
But before we jump
into the questions,

00:27:24.580 --> 00:27:28.270
we wanted to leave you
with a few key takeaways

00:27:28.270 --> 00:27:30.220
around our talk.

